    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>Demo Game </strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo you will be able to choose the first two stages, which include the search for an egg and the search for salt and potatoes. Also you will be introduced how to cook the menus after gaining the ingredients. to gain the ingredients you need to collect money to buy them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you take some persons from the market by slapping them with the handbag, they'll get you some exitementpoints. these are used to grab in your bag and pick a new upgrade or skill. (Vampire Survivor like)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls are movement and the button (A) for actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest of the earned money after a run is your meta currency. You can use it to buy new bags with new skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The progression will not transfer to the full game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since this is not the final version, it may differ from V 1.0.<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grandma found an amazing new recipe in a magazine and is so excited to cook it!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She's heading to the market to get all the ingredients she needs.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What could possibly go wrong? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Menu</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/16777e4eaf29b7e1f9562cecb2e7fa91.poster.avif?t=1740446471\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/16777e4eaf29b7e1f9562cecb2e7fa91.webm?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/16777e4eaf29b7e1f9562cecb2e7fa91.mp4?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many retirees enjoy relaxing in their rocking chair, flipping through different magazines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Shop</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/c55a8bda1523db4fb918189145b1f153.poster.avif?t=1740446471\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/c55a8bda1523db4fb918189145b1f153.webm?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/c55a8bda1523db4fb918189145b1f153.mp4?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It would be fair to say that shopping is a pastime enjoyed by many people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One might therefore ask whether the prices on different markets are consistent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Handbag</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8a4d4f70210407e32335793d85d48df2.poster.avif?t=1740446471\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8a4d4f70210407e32335793d85d48df2.webm?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8a4d4f70210407e32335793d85d48df2.mp4?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is certainly conceivable that the universe contained within a handbag  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is one that is still largely unexplored. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Bingo</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/380162e89760804d5e627e1ea1a055c2.poster.avif?t=1740446471\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/380162e89760804d5e627e1ea1a055c2.webm?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/380162e89760804d5e627e1ea1a055c2.mp4?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you enter a store, you have the chance to win a prize.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy more tickets if you want. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>Cooking</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8bced7c0427e1afe3e09b1156cf5aced.poster.avif?t=1740446471\" width=594 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8bced7c0427e1afe3e09b1156cf5aced.webm?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285560/extras/8bced7c0427e1afe3e09b1156cf5aced.mp4?t=1740446471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grandma is a passionate cook who loves to make awesome food! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>And more is coming!!</u></i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi, thanks for your interest in my new game. I'm currently putting it together. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm always happy when someone adds my product to their wish list. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'll keep you updated on the latest developments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Until then, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Velemir</p>",
